  <div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h2 style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;"><strong>A Taste of Sweden: Authentic Swedish Candy</strong></h2></div>

  <style></style>
</div></div></div></div><div class="fe-block fe-block-7efc3332efa6f6db0d9f-1"><div class="sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block" data-block-css="[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/2310c5bc-514f-40b3-91a5-4c7819684138_298/website.components.html.styles.css&quot;]" data-block-scripts="[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/2310c5bc-514f-40b3-91a5-4c7819684138_298/website.components.html.visitor.js&quot;]" data-block-type="1337" data-definition-name="website.components.html" data-sqsp-block="text" id="block-7efc3332efa6f6db0d9f-1"><div class="sqs-block-content"><div class="sqs-text-block-container">
  
  <div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class=""><span class="sqsrte-text-color--black">Experience the magic of <strong>Swedish candy in Tampa</strong>! Our store offers a delightful selection of traditional Swedish treats, including licorice, gummy candies and chocolates, all made with the highest quality ingredients. Whether you're craving the bold flavors of salty licorice or the sweetness of Swedish gummy candies, every bite is a trip to Sweden. Visit us in Tampa or order online for <strong>nationwide delivery</strong> and indulge in the authentic taste of Swedish candy that will leave your taste buds wanting more! With <strong>shipping available across the U.S.</strong>, you can enjoy a sweet slice of Sweden wherever you are.</span></p></div>

  <style></style>
</div></div></div></div><div class="fe-block fe-block-5b6dad964922038aa931"><div class="sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-image image-block" data-aspect-ratio="61.08041463080506" data-block-css="[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.imageFluid/6ed13754-14b4-4e56-af15-758015d2d4b7_286/website.components.imageFluid.styles.css&quot;]" data-block-scripts="[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.imageFluid/6ed13754-14b4-4e56-af15-758015d2d4b7_286/website.components.imageFluid.shared.constants.js&quot;,&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.imageFluid/6ed13754-14b4-4e56-af15-758015d2d4b7_286/748.js&quot;,&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.imageFluid/6ed13754-14b4-4e56-af15-758015d2d4b7_286/8018.js&quot;,&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.imageFluid/6ed13754-14b4-4e56-af15-758015d2d4b7_286/9882.js&quot;,&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.imageFluid/6ed13754-14b4-4e56-af15-758015d2d4b7_286/image-effect-film-grain.js&quot;,&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.imageFluid/6ed13754-14b4-4e56-af15-758015d2d4b7_286/image-effect-liquid.js&quot;,&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.imageFluid/6ed13754-14b4-4e56-af15-758015d2d4b7_286/image-effect-parallax.js&quot;,&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.imageFluid/6ed13754-14b4-4e56-af15-758015d2d4b7_286/image-effect-refracted-circles.js&quot;,&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.component