  <div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h1 style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Who We Are</h1></div>

  <style></style>
</div></div></div></div><div class="fe-block fe-block-de55b46ddd6702dbea04"><div class="sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block" data-block-css="[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/2310c5bc-514f-40b3-91a5-4c7819684138_298/website.components.html.styles.css&quot;]" data-block-scripts="[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/2310c5bc-514f-40b3-91a5-4c7819684138_298/website.components.html.visitor.js&quot;]" data-block-type="1337" data-definition-name="website.components.html" data-sqsp-block="text" id="block-de55b46ddd6702dbea04"><div class="sqs-block-content"><div class="sqs-text-block-container">
  
  <div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">We are true candy lovers, who know the essence of Saturday Sweets (Lördagsgodis in Swedish), a tradition where all kids have a right to enjoy their sweets after a long-week of hard work!</p></div>

  <style></style>
